routeFacts.name: Rhein-Ruhr Osten
routeFacts.description: The Rhein-Ruhr Osten route is a German route for Train Sim World. It features the 42-kilometre route between Hagen HBF and Wuppertal-Steinbeck, featuring both the mainline and S-Bahn route. The MRCE BR 185.5 and DB BR 422 are both featured with this route.
routeInfo: The route runs from Hagen HBF to Wuppertal-Steinbeck, including both the mainline used by freight services and the S-Bahn route via Gevelsberg. Together these lines have a total route length of 42 kilometres. The route is mostly double track though there are some single track sections.
